class=3D"Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>to complete the =
walk-through and determine the scope-of-works for the repairs to your =
home.<o:p></o:p></span></div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt; =
font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;">Once we have completed this document =E2=80=93 I can return =
and go through each item on the scope line-by-line in detail with you so =
you can gain the confidence that we have captured =
everything.<o:p></o:p></span></div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: =
11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-family: =
Aptos, sans-serif;">When we go through the scope together =E2=80=93 we =
can consider adding anything further that is necessary if we need to. I =
am exceptionally confident that Stephen and I will capture everything on =
the first draft =E2=80=93 but I want you to know that you will sign-off =
on the scope-of-works as being complete before we move to the repair =
phase.<o:p></o:p></span></div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: =
11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-family: =
Aptos, sans-serif;">You do not need to join us for today=E2=80=99s visit =
=E2=80=93 but you are more than welcome to if you wish. As I stated =E2=80=
=93 we can review it together once complete. I will let you decide =
whether you wish to join us or not.<o:p></o:p></span></div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">Please do =
not hesitate to contact me if you have any questions or concerns at =
all.<o:p></o:p></span></div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt; =
